			"compact mode doesn't break layouts — some components may need min-height or text truncation adjustments",
			"FIDC users prefer compact — validate with FIDC gestor feedback after deployment",
		]
		rationale: "Token-driven 2024+. Token extraction is one-time investment. ROI: immediate (42h vs 80-120h for same result). Plus: every future density/theme change is configuration (minutes), not code (hours). Tokens are infrastructure — invest once, benefit forever."
